macro.title: More Home Sellers Test the Market, But Buyers Aren’t Budging
macro.what: Pending home sales are declining, with some house hunters waiting for mortgage rates to drop lower and some feeling jittery about the economy
macro.why: Rates & inflation shape discount rates and housing affordability.
macro.market: Lower rates support demand/valuations; higher rates pressure builders/REITs and slow transactions.
